headline: Xcel Energy Inc. Board Declares Dividend on Common Stock
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, December 18, 2024--The Board of Directors of Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) today declared a quarterly dividend on its common stock of 54.75 cents per share. The dividends are payable January 20, 2025, to shareholders of record on January 6, 2025.
